aVand then from there it just soared.
p175
aVI mean, from there my treatment just when out of sight,
p176
aVbecause they were like, Kurt, explain this, explain this.
p177
aVAnd for the first time in 23 years,
p178
aVI could actually talk about stuff openly to, like, anybody.
p179
aVI could talk to you about it right now if I wanted to,
p180
aVbecause it unlocked it.
p181
aVIt's just amazing.
p182
aVAnd it allowed me to put 23 years of PTSD
p183
aVand TBI stuff together in one place
